            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
              <para>
                <text><changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Subsections (1) and (2)</citation></changeable> are subject to the trustees providing to the Crown a registrable covenant in relation to the site—</text>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>for the preservation of the reserve and conservation values of that land and public access; and</text>
                  </para>
                </label-para>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>as set out in Part 11 of the Schedule of the deed of settlement (the <def-term id="DLM2274936">Waimahora Stream site covenant</def-term>).</text>
                  </para>
                </label-para>
              </para>
            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">4</label>
              <para>
                <text>The Waimahora Stream site covenant is to be treated as a conservation covenant for the purposes of—</text>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>section 77 of the Reserves Act 1977:</text>
                  </para>
                </label-para>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>section 27 of the Conservation Act 1987.</text>
                  </para>
                </label-para>
              </para>
            </subprov>
          </prov.body>
        </prov>
        <prov id="DLM2274937" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">46</label>
          <heading>Lake Hickson site</heading>
          <prov.body>
