                <text>The fee simple estate in the Ruatangata site vests in the trustees.</text>
              </para>
            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
              <para>
                <text><changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Subsection (1)</citation></changeable> is subject to the trustees providing the Crown with—</text>
                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>a registrable right of way easement in gross in favour of the New Zealand Railways Corporation over the area shown marked B on SO 417422 and on the terms and conditions set out in Part 12 of the Schedule of the deed of settlement (the <emphasis style="bold">Ruatangata site easement</emphasis>); and</text>
