                <label-para skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>a registrable right to convey electricity in gross in favour of Powerco Limited over the areas shown marked B and G on SO 417422 and on the terms and conditions set out in Part 12A of the Schedule of the deed of settlement (the <emphasis style="bold">Ruatangata electricity easement</emphasis>)</text>
