                    <entry colsep="0" rowsep="0">Pukepuke Lagoon House site</entry>
                    <entry colsep="0" rowsep="0"/>
                    <entry colsep="0" rowsep="0">0.27 hectares, approximately, being Part Section 798 Town of Carnarvon. Part <emphasis style="italic">Gazette</emphasis> 1869 p 544. Subject to survey.</entry>
